  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of coconut oil in a large wok or skillet over high heat.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and stir-fry until fragrant, about 30 seconds.",
    "Add the Brussels sprouts and stir-fry until they start to char, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the binchotan charcoal and stir-fry for another 2 minutes.",
    "Add the fish sauce, lime juice, sambal chili paste, sugar, Vietnamese chili flakes, salt, and black pepper, and stir-fry for another minute.",
    "Transfer the wok or skillet to the binchotan charcoal grill and cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Serve the well-charred Brussels sprouts hot with steamed bun and sweet chili sauce."
